metadata.name: Shade #1
metadata.description: In a world where both sides try to claim the throne, constant battle is the result. Good vs Evil, only one can be victorious. Light is at the end of the tunnel, but in order to reach the ether you must pass the shadows. Nothing good comes easy, the path to nirvana has its setbacks. Souls are transformed to Shade and connect with their companions for the first time. Depending on how one lived their mortal existence, they are matched with either an angel or a demon. Members of Shade lock horns to figure out who makes it to the final chapter. Enter, Shade NFT.
